Description: The arpwatch package contains arpwatch and arpsnmp.  Arpwatch and
           : arpsnmp are both network monitoring tools.  Both utilities monitor
           : Ethernet or FDDI network traffic and build databases of Ethernet/IP
           : address pairs, and can report certain changes via email.
           : 
           : Install the arpwatch package if you need networking monitoring
           : devices which will automatically keep track of the IP addresses on
           : your network.

